Business Development Manager Job in Dubai
Salary: AED 15000Posted: 3 days ago
Responsibilities:
Overall responsibility of sales and marketing activities for OPTICON
Construction ERP in Gulf countries.
* Responsibility to achieve the sales target set by company.
* Location will be UAE and travel across all Emirates.
Prospecting clients in the construction industry - contractors, real estate developers, construction enterprises
Leads generation, client meetings, making presentations, handling techno commercial discussions, negotiations, closing the deals and ensuring timely payments from customers.
Prepare and submit proposals to clients as per company norms and procedures.
Develop and manage the funnel of opportunities and coordinate with implementation team.
Graduate or Post-graduate in Engineering/ Marketing from reputed institute.
10+ years of related experience in sales and business development in software industry or construction domain, international business development experience will be preferred.
Knowledge and contacts within construction industry in gulf countries preferred.
Candidates having previous experience in middle east and having valid UAE driving license shall be given preference.
Deep understanding of selling Enterprise Software Solutions (ERP). This includes marketing strategy and tactics, product demonstration, sales techniques, and CRM.
Possess a pro-active work attitude with good interpersonal
and
communication skills.
Mature and independent, should be able to manage his own time.
